name: GET 211 Listings
docs:
(Not presently used by client app)

This endpoint gets all the listings from the load_211 table in our database that has been loaded from the LA Open Data Portal 211 API.

The 211.org site has been re-designed since the data was imported, and we have not re-implemeted an import process to re-import the data, so the data is stale.

name: Get Open LA Listings
docs:
(Not presently used by client app)

This endpoint gets all the listings from the load_open_la_data  import table in our database. This was imported from the Open LA Data Portal.

The data was imported with a one-time import process (not sure what the procedure was)

name: Get LA Regional Food Bank Listings
docs:
(Not presently used by client app)

This endpoint gets all the listings from the load_larfb  import table in our database. This was imported from a massaged Google Sheet based on a csv file received form thr LA Regional Food Bank.
